doc: Suggest excluding libtestutils for !jsonrpc/headlines configuration. FixedWebThreeServer.h is only included by ethrpctest and not used elsewhere. json-rpc doesn't need to be a dependency of libtestutils if it's only used by ethrpctest (class can be moved). If nothing uses jsonrpc from libtestutils, can FixedWebThreeServer.h be moved to ethrpctest?
